Chuck Allie (born at June 2, 1988 in Making, Parang, Maguindanao) is a Filipino actor. He became famous after joining StarStruck: The Nationwide Invasion where he finished as the last Avenger. He was first paired with Iwa Moto before with Jana Roxas.
